properties.title: Java date and time API - Time Zones
properties.author: Brian S O'Neill

section.name: Available Time Zones
section.p: Time zone data is provided by the public IANA time zone database. The following table shows all the time zones supported by Joda-Time, using version 2018g of the database. It is also possible to update to a later version of the database. This table can be rebuilt by running org.joda.example.time.TimeZoneTable.

tr.td: Etc/GMT+0, Etc/GMT-0, Etc/GMT0, Etc/Greenwich, GMT, GMT+0, GMT-0, GMT0, Greenwich
